| wchar\_t/char<sup>1</sup>         | Char                                                             | Char                    | readChar/writeChar                           |
| wchar\_t\*/char\*<sup>1</sup>     | string                                                           | string                  | readString/writeString                       |
| double                            | Double                                                           | double                  | readDouble/writeDouble                       |
| float                             | float                                                            | float                   | readFloat/writeFloat                         |
